edu.jhu.rebar.ingest

Class TweetInfoJsonReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.rebar.ingest.TweetInfoJsonReader

  • public class TweetInfoJsonReader
extends Object
    Class used to read in a JSON Tweet record and convert it to a rebar protobuf object (Concrete.TweetInfo). The input JSON record should use the standard twitter API, as defined at: https://dev.twitter.com/docs/platform-objects/tweets
